_sText:
Made by night-terror
steam name is runie360 if u need help with map or want to report a bug
have fun!

this map is symetrical. both teams are equal
in the middle of the map there is a large white tower, on top of it is about 10 grenades and
a m249. whoever gets there first controlls the map.

the glass splitting the play are is thin and you can shoot thru it. if you dont feel like going
to get the m249 you can take cover behind crates as you shoot the other team.

enjoy the map!
